values: I am sooooo pissed off at guys right now!! I dont understand yall fuckers at all and I am really mad and venting... OH and dont worry this only goes towards a couple of guys. If you flirt with us why dont you ask us out... its not like your dating anyone else... OR ARE YOU??? Screw you I dont know why I look out for people and then they ignore you... it really pisses me off... guys are my weakness and I thought that I had finally found one that was right for me... no matter age, but I was wrong! Age does matter because you are a jerk and a bitch so therefore... dont ever talk to me again if you are going to be a bitch and ignore me! Im sorry im not a sweet lil angel, sorry I have issues, sorry Im not a girly girl! If you want me you have to except me the way I am!! Why am I changing for you... I really liked you, but you cant get it right huh?? Fuckin Bitch!! Dont even talk to me or try to talk to me... BYE FOREVER BITCH!!

ok... so can anyone see me working any where else??  I went to a church function last weekend in San Antonio and I was worshiping with all my heart... and I figured out that my job was a bad influence to my life.  I love my job to death and I love all the peole I work with but it is a horrrible influence to me.  I want to cry... I dont know what to do... PLEASE pray for me and help me make my decision... THANK YOU... love you all lots... BYE!!

I have two great best friends, well at least I thought they were great, who have been keeping secrets from me cuz they are not sure how I react.  They told me today and I was fine with what they yold me, but I was upset that they didn't tell me sooner.  They told eachother but didn't want to tell me... I had to keep asking them what they were hiding from me.  I am really pissed off now just thinking about it because best friends should not be keeping secrets from eachother especially when they know me like they do.  I just don't get it and UHHH  OMG... I just want to yell at them and tell them how much that hurt me and disgusted me!  I dunno but I may have to back off from them for a while so I could calm down and stuff... I am so freakin' frustrated... I dunno!  What should I do?  Seriously... what... I am so confused and dazed that they would do this to me.  Well, I am done venting so I guess I'm done.  Sorry if this seems stupid but I gotta do what I gotta do.  Check yall later... BYE!
